    "about_the_developer": "About the Developer",
    "kaamkaaz_is_designed_and_developed": "Kaamkaaz is designed and developed by Ankit Yadav, an independent software developer based in Rajasthan, India. Devoted to creating digital tools that solve real-world problems for rural and semi-urban populations.",
    "location": "Location:",
