    "at_kaamkaaz_we_are_dedicated": "At Kaamkaaz, we are dedicated to building a trusted community that connects daily wage earners and recruiters across India. These Community Guidelines are designed to ensure safety, mutual respect, and fairness for every user. By using our platform, you agree to abide by these standards.",
    "1_general_rules_for_everyone": "1. General Rules for Everyone",
    "respect_and_dignity_treat_all": "Respect and Dignity: Treat all users with courtesy, regardless of their background, gender, caste, religion, or language.",
    "honesty_and_integrity_provide_completely": "Honesty and Integrity: Provide completely truthful profile details, skill descriptions, KYC documents, and wage quotes.",
    "legal_compliance_do_not_use": "Legal Compliance: Do not use the platform to violate any local, state, or national laws, including minimum wage codes.",
